body_html:
I met the same issue. I always using NDK 17 without any error, but today pull the latest source, the issue happen.
[update]: the issue happen on android_arm64-v8a. (e.g. bazel build --cxxopt='--std=c++11' -c opt --config=android_arm64-v8a tensorflow/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model)
There's no any issue on android_armeabi-v7a. (e.g. bazel build --cxxopt='--std=c++11' -c opt --config=android_armeabi-v7a tensorflow/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model)

I met the same issue. I always using NDK 17 without any error, but today pull the latest source, the issue happen.
[update]: the issue happen on android_arm64-v8a.  (e.g. bazel build --cxxopt='--std=c++11' -c opt --config=android_arm64-v8a tensorflow/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model)
There's no any issue on android_armeabi-v7a. (e.g.  bazel build --cxxopt='--std=c++11' -c opt --config=android_armeabi-v7a tensorflow/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model)
